T01TD1116E:62b-3: de kho na nyid la bstod pa /
T01TD1116E:62b-4: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1116E:62b-5: thogs pa kun las rnam grol ba //
T01TD1116E:62b-6: kha dog bral zhing ma skyes shing //
T01TD1116E:62b-7: rang gi ngo bo 'jig med pa'i //
T01TD1116E:62b-8: sku mnga' de bzhin gshegs phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1116E:62b-9: nyon mongs rags dang phra spangs pa //
T01TD1116E:62b-10: bdag gis mi mnga' sgrib pa dag / dang po yod pas stong pa'i phyir //
T01TD1116E:62b-11: don dam mkha' dkyil 'dra phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1116E:62b-12: rnam rtog sprul ni spangs pas na //
T01TD1116E:62b-13: ci dgyes par ni mdzad gyur pa //
T01TD1116E:62b-14: gter mchog de nyid rtag gzigs pa //
T01TD1116E:62b-16: rnam par rtog pa thams cad spangs //
T01TD1116E:62b-17: nyid kyis dgyes bdar ma byas sku //
T01TD1116E:62b-18: 'khor dang zhi bar ro mnyam sku //
T01TD1116E:62b-19: rnam rtog dri ma med phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1116E:62b-20: yang dag dgongs pas mnal mi mnga' //
T01TD1116E:62b-21: gti mug bral zhing spangs pas bzhugs //
T01TD1116E:62b-22: rtag tu de nyid ma gsal ba //
T01TD1116E:62b-23: rang bzhin mkhas pas shar phyag 'tshal ;
T01TD1116E:62b-24: / bsam gtan tshes grangs yongs rdzogs pas //
T01TD1116E:62b-25: mi rnams dga' ba skyed mdzad pa //
T01TD1116E:62b-26: rnam grol zla ba yid 'ong ba //
T01TD1116E:62b-27: lta ngan rab rib sel phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1116E:62b-28: dngos po dngos med gnyis 'das nas //
T01TD1116E:62b-29: rtog pa'i dri ma las grol ba //
T01TD1116E:62b-30: rtsen dor med nges mnyam gnas //
T01TD1116E:63a-0: @63a * // spros mi mnga' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T01TD1116E:63a-1: dri med chu rlabs bde ba'i rgyu //
T01TD1116E:63a-2: ma lus srog chags 'tsho mdzad pa //
T01TD1116E:63a-3: che zhing mtha' med tshad dang bral //
T01TD1116E:63a-4: de nyid rgya mtsho che phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1116E:63a-5: legs spyad du ma rgyas thob pa //
T01TD1116E:63a-6: dpe med ro zhim yid la 'bab //
T01TD1116E:63a-7: rga shi'i 'jigs pa med mdzad pa //
T01TD1116E:63a-8: de nyid bdud rtsi la phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1116E:63a-9: rang gi yid la brtan ldan yang //
T01TD1116E:63a-10: khyab 'jug dbang phyug tshangs dbang dang //
T01TD1116E:63a-11: lha dang drang srong thabs med pa //
T01TD1116E:63a-12: thabs de skad cig brnyes phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1116E:63a-13: dri med rin thang mnyam med pa //
T01TD1116E:63a-14: ngo bos 'dod rnams yongs rdzogs mdzad //
T01TD1116E:63a-15: bsod nams bsags pas dmigs gyur pa //
T01TD1116E:63a-16: yid bzhin byang chub sems phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1116E:63a-17: srid pa'i 'khor bas yongs dub pa'i //
T01TD1116E:63a-18: mchog tu lta ba bde ba'i gnas //
T01TD1116E:63a-19: byang chub yan lag me tog ldan //
T01TD1116E:63a-20: zhi ba'i dpag bsam shing phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1116E:63a-21: shes bya shes med gnyis med cing //
T01TD1116E:63a-22: phra sbom dbye ba rnams las grol //
T01TD1116E:63a-23: sna tshogs dpe las 'das gyur pa //
T01TD1116E:63a-24: tshig gis brjod mi nus phyag 'tshal //
T01TD1116E:63a-25: rtag tu rgyal zhing bsnyengs mi mnga' //
T01TD1116E:63a-26: gzhan stobs 'joms byed mdud pa med //
T01TD1116E:63a-27: gnyis med sku mnga' bsam mi khyab //
T01TD1116E:63a-29: bye brag med par dbang 'gyur zhing //
T01TD1116E:63a-30: dngos tshogs skad cig la bsregs pa //
T01TD1116E:63a-31: shin tu drag pa'i rang bzhin gyis //
T01TD1116E:63a-33: 'di ltar yang dag bstod las dge ba gang thob pa'i //
T01TD1116E:63a-34: bsod nams des ni 'gro ba ma lus zad 'gyur zhing //
T01TD1116E:63a-35: sems can rnams ni sdug bsngal dag dang bral gyur pa //
T01TD1116E:63a-36: bde ba dang ldan sgrib med mya ngan 'das thob shog / de kho na nyid la bstod pa sh'akya'i dge slong dpal gyi go chas mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T01TD1116E:63a-38: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po manydzu shr'i bha dra dang /
T01TD1116E:63a-39: dge slong sh'akya 'od kyis bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la phab pa//
